overview:
DeQeo Consulting is an International Education Consultancy that facilitates the gaining of admission into universities abroad, we are a Study Abroad Agency.

We don’t just provide admission letters, we assess and assist the students right from the point of first interest up until they arrive in their destination country and settle fully and legally.

We work closely with each student and directly with the universities we represent in other to ensure that students are matched rightly based on their preferences and need to a suitable institution.

Our success is driven by the dedication and diligence of our staff who have first-hand experience in living and studying abroad, as well as our experienced and passionate partners.
